[gd_scene load_steps=17 format=3 uid="uid://b0embergrave_s1room02_wide_chunk"]

; S1 bigger-rooms retrofit Stage 1A (ticket 86ca3kpzz). Hand-widened proof
; chunk: 30x8 tiles = 960x256 px (vs the 15x8 / 480x256 single-screen chunks).
; Drives the camera-scroll machinery: with world bounds wider than the
; viewport, CameraDirector.set_world_bounds takes the SCROLL branch (not the
; centre branch) so the camera follows the player across the wider floor.
; Reuses the S1CloisterChunk painter (grid_w=30 override) + the warm flat
; floor PNG absorbed from PR #403. Wall collision perimeter + seams + props
; redistributed across the wider span. ONE proof chunk only (OOS: widening all
; 8 rooms / procgen — see ticket).
;
; Decoration-density pass (ticket 86ca3yuwv, Uma brief
; team/uma-ux/s1-decoration-density.md). "A hall built for a crowd that no
; longer comes" — decorated rails (N + S wall bands) + corner pockets, with a
; swept-clear central aisle (y 112-176) for traversal + combat. Reuse-only
; first pass: activates the 3 approved-but-unused props (brazier_cold,
; banner_worn, pillar_arch) + adds existing moss/parchment/rubble. 9 -> 23
; props. KEEP-CLEAR honored exactly (chunk-def-traced): lane y 112-176, both
; ports, RoomGate(48,144), 4 grunt-spawn tiles (336,112)/(496,176)/(688,112)/
; (816,176) at ~48px radius. DECORATION Sprite2D nodes ONLY — no collision /
; wall-perimeter / spawn / gate / fountain changes.

