; --- Decoration-density pass (86ca3yuwv) — new reuse-only props below ---
; Warmth gradient: lit N wall (braziers above) -> clear aisle -> dimmer S wall
; (cold brazier + heavier moss/rubble). Pillars flank the aisle (make it a
; HALL). Banners line the N wall between braziers. Corners settle rubble /
; parchment / moss. Every coord checked vs keep-clear: lane y 112-176, spawn
; tiles +/-48px, both ports, RoomGate swept area.

; North wall band — 2 hanging banners, staggered between the lit braziers
; (braziers at x=160/400/640/840; banners between, NOT aligned — anti-tiling).
